```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(srvyr)
library(janitor)
library(dplyr)
census <- read_csv("poverty1.csv")
census <- census [9:63 , 1:5] %>%
  na.omit() %>%
  rename(total_pop = 2) %>%
  rename(in_poverty = 3) %>%
  rename(moe = 4) %>%
  rename(percent_poverty = 5)
view(census)
```
